General.Name: Borneo Oil Bhd
General.Description: Borneo Oil Berhad, an investment holding company, operates and franchises fast food restaurants in Malaysia and Australia. It operates through Food and Franchise Operations; Property Investment and Management; and Resources and Sustainable Energy segments. The company is also involved in the mining operations and related activities; property management, plantation, construction, and related activities; trading of construction materials; oil, gas, and energy and its related businesses; agricultural and farming activities for crops production; and supply of raw foods and food products. In addition, it manufactures, sells, and distributes products; provides management and marketing services; and supplies franchise equipment and spare parts. The company was formerly known as Sugar Bun Corporation Berhad and changed its name to Borneo Oil Berhad in January 2007. Borneo Oil Berhad was founded in 1984 and is based in Kuching, Malaysia.
